Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Description: DTwrappers provides wrapper functions that aim to simplify the syntax of the data.table package.  The wrapper functions facilitate usage of a range of data.table's core features.  Furthermore, the methods are also built to demonstrate how to write effective data.table statements for educational purposes in a wide variety of settings.
